export const symbols = {
    White: "w",
    Blue: "u",
    Black: "b",
    Red: "r",
    Green: "g",

    HybridWU: "wu",
    HybridWB: "wb",
    HybridRW: "rw",
    HybridRG: "rg",
    HybridGU: "gu",
    HybridGW: "gw",
    HybridUB: "ub",
    HybridUR: "ur",
    HybridBR: "br",
    HybridBG: "bg",

    // mana font does not support more than 2 colorless and color split. (ex 3/W is not supported)
    TWhite: "2w",
    TBlue: "2u",
    TBlack: "2b",
    TRed: "2r",
    TGreen: "2g",

    // 
    PhyWhite: "wp",
    PhyBlue: "up",
    PhyBlack: "bp",
    PhyRed: "rp",
    PhyGreen: "gp",
    PhyHybrid: "wup",
}
